[[span class="bt"]]Obtain The Leading Edge:[[/span]] A legendary blade, woven into the pataphysical folds of reality; its wielder embodies the Spirit of the Hero. The nature of this weapon would allow for SCP-6500 to be overcome with the resolution of a grand quest.
