[[span class="bt"]]Collect the Oriykalkos Codex:[[/span]] a mystical artefact capable of storing vast amounts of magical energy and allowing its user to perform rites and rituals on a potentially-universal scale. Thaumic workings using the Codex would be capable of halting and reversing the effects of SCP-6500 altogether.
[[/div]]

[[/tab]]

